Privacy PolicyJOG ProductionEffective 

JOG Production our is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our application ("App"). By using the App, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

1. Information We Do Not Collect

JOG Production does not collect, store, or share any personal user data. Our App is designed for internal use by authorized personnel only.

2. User Access and Authentication

Access to the App is granted through a unique ID and password provided by the administrator.

No external users can create an account or access the App.

3. Data Usage and Processing

The App is used to manage inventory, stock-in, forecast orders, material requests, and no-code requests.

All data processed within the App remains secure and is only accessible to authorized users.

4. Third-Party Services

The App does not integrate with any third-party services that collect personal data.

Any external services used are strictly for operational purposes within the organization.

5. Security Measures

We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure the security of data processed within the App.

Only authorized users can access and manage the App's functionalities.

6. Compliance with Legal Obligations

We comply with applicable laws and regulations regarding data protection and security.

Since no personal user data is collected, there are no data retention or deletion policies applicable.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be communicated through the App or other appropriate channels. Continued use of the App after modifications indicates acceptance of the revised policy.

8. Contact Information

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:Email: ravish@jogdigitalinnovations.com

By using the App, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy.

